(33540, 91296, 0, 1, 'memorie lies in the past(搶鮮聽)', '', '2011-03-05 00:00:00', 2000, 0, 2, 7, '迷失方向的路上 該如何操縱去向\r\n\r\ni lost my WAY On the road i don,t know how to control\r\n\r\n用身命的力量 現在在何方 \r\n\r\now with the power of life *can''t find where to belong) \r\n\r\n\r\n*我要抓住夢想\r\n(I want to grab my dream )\r\n\r\n傷口持續在漫延 眼前的畫面我看不見 \r\n\r\nthe scar still burning and i can,t see everything i,m not afraid \r\n\r\n*回憶停留在從前\r\n(memorie lies in the past)\r\n\r\n我向前衝 不留下任何遺憾\r\nI sprint forward leaving no regret\r\n*我想重生 來讓你了解\r\n(I want to born again \r\nTo let you understand)\r\n*我想在我生命中永不後悔 \r\n(I never want to regret in my life)\r\n\r\n即使破碎的世界 總是充滿虛假\r\nEven shattered world Always filled with lies \r\n\r\nnaver to cry(絕不哭泣)......\r\n\r\n要我怎樣你才明白 我的無奈 \r\nHow did you want me to understand my frustration\r\n\r\n告訴我你是情緒失控 才讓我走 \r\nTell me you''re feeling out of control before I go\r\n\r\n告訴我你會回來\r\ntall me you will come back\r\n\r\n你叫我要如何面對 你的依賴 \r\ntold me you have to rely on how to face\r\n\r\n告訴我你會回來\r\ntall me you will come back\r\n\r\n讓我失控做出一切 我也不後悔 \r\nLet me make all out of control I do not regret it\r\n\r\n告訴我你會回來\r\ntall me you will come back\r\n\r\n', '', 148, '', '桃利煬', '桃利煬', 'Ｅ = ＭｘＣ平方 ', 'Ｅ = ＭｘＣ平方 ', '', 0, 0, 0, '2011-03-05 00:09:10', '2015-03-12 13:46:14', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
